8Jh4 |archive-date=14 April 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{flagdeco|TUR}} <!---deleting from Europe will be considered vandalism and will lead to blocking of account and IP---> [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Turkey|Turkey]]\n|82,329\n|1,890\n|10,453\n|<ref>{{cite web |url=https://covid19.tubitak.gov.tr/turkiyede-durum |title=T\u00fcrkiye'de Durum |website=covid19.tubitak.gov.tr/ |access-date=27 March 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200326162202/https://covid19.tubitak.gov.tr/turkiyede-durum |archive-date=26 March 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{flagdeco|BEL}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Belgium|Belgium]]\n|38,496\n|5,683\n|8,757\n|<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.info-coronavirus.be/nl/news/ |title=Coronavirus COVID-19 |website=www.info-coronavirus.be |language=fr |access-date=11 March 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200319151913/https://www.info-coronavirus.be/nl/news/ |archive-date=19 March 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{flagdeco|RUS}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Russia|Russia]]\n|36,793\n|313\n|3,057\n|\n|-\n|{{flagdeco|NLD}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in the Netherlands|Netherlands]]\n|32,655\n|3,684\n|\n|<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rivm.nl/nieuws/actuele-informatie-over-coronavirus |title=Actuele informatie over het nieuwe coronavirus (COVID-19) {{!}} RIVM |website=www.rivm.nl |access-date=11 March 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200321131517/https://www.rivm.nl/nieuws/actuele-informatie-over-coronavirus |archive-date=21 March 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{flagdeco|CHE}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Switzerland|Switzerland]]\n|27,201\n|1,368\n|17,100\n|<ref>{{cite web |url=https://interactif.tdg.ch/2020/covid-19-carte-suisse/ |title=Cas d'infection au Sars-CoV-2 en Suisse |website=tdg.ch |language=fr |access-date=10 April 2020 |archive-url=http://archive.is/wip/bR2QA |archive-date=10 April 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{flagdeco|PRT}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in 